Revision history for Perl extension Mail::vpopmail.

0.60 Mon Apr 16 00:32:24 EDT 2007
   - added sql support (thanks to Werner Garcia for hints)
   - removed legacy "get" function left over from v0.52
   - changed alldomains behavior
     * ->map returns a hash reference of domain name -> domain directory
     * ->dir returns an array refrence of all domain directories

0.54 Wed Dec  6 15:14:22 EST 2006
   - added dir field to domaininfo

0.53 Tue Oct 17 20:45:21 EDT 2006
   - updated forgotten Constructor documentation 
     (such as userinfo, domaininfo and alldomains)

0.52 Fri Sep 29 15:23:41 EDT 2006
   - added feature to get all mailboxes in a domain
   - added feature to get all properties of a domain
	- added feature to get all domains
	- added feature to get all domains and their directories

0.51 Thu Sep 15 20:35:06 EDT 2005
   - enabled compatiblity for vpopmail installations compiled
     with --disable-clear-passwd

0.50  Mon Dec 13 21:44:37 2004
	- original version; created by h2xs 1.21 with options
		-AX Mail::vpopmail

